		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not quite NES but Hitoshi Sakimoto's early work on the Genesis had a bit of it mainly in the pulse channels. Thinking Devlish. Also, the gamegear port of that and Gunstar Heroes were loaded with arps.

		

